OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F334A1783703991
OL,3,CThe 'excruciating' reality of Stiff
OL,4,CPerson Syndrome
OL,6,FA man is calling for greater awareness
OL,7,Fof the extremely rare disorder which
OL,8,Fcauses him uncontrollable spasms that
OL,9,Fleave him "like a statue".
OL,11,FIan Rawlins, 62, has Stiff Person
OL,12,FSyndrome (SPS), a neurological and
OL,13,Fautoimmune condition which affects
OL,14,Fbetween one in 100,000 and one in one
OL,15,Fmillion people worldwide.
OL,17,FHe suffers from daily spasms, which
OL,18,Fcause his body to become rigid.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,335,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F334A1783703991
OL,3,CThe 'excruciating' reality of Stiff
OL,4,CPerson Syndrome
OL,6,FThe former lorry driver, from
OL,7,FBarnsley, said: "They're excruciating.
OL,8,FIt's absolute agony. It's frightening
OL,9,Fbecause I can't breathe.
OL,11,F"It just takes over your body. Every
OL,12,Fmuscle in the body is in spasm. Once
OL,13,Feverything sort of settles, my eyes
OL,14,Fshut, I can't open my eyes. So, it
OL,15,Flooks like I'm asleep, but I'm not.
OL,16,FI'm rigid, like a statue, I just
OL,17,Fcannot move and I can be like that for
OL,18,Fhours."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,335,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F334A1783703991
OL,3,CThe 'excruciating' reality of Stiff
OL,4,CPerson Syndrome
OL,6,FMr Rawlins' wife Andrea said: "I am
OL,7,Fabsolutely helpless to help him, I
OL,8,Fcan't do anything. I've tried to
OL,9,Fadminister medication, but it will not
OL,10,Fwork quickly enough."
OL,12,FResearchers do not know the exact
OL,13,Fcause of SPS, but the condition causes
OL,14,Fthe immune system to attack healthy
OL,15,Fcells.
OL,17,FMr Rawlins' episodes can be triggered
OL,18,Fby sudden noise and bright or flashing
OL,19,Flights.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,335,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F334A1783703991
OL,3,CThe 'excruciating' reality of Stiff
OL,4,CPerson Syndrome
OL,6,F"If someone touches me, sort of makes
OL,7,Fme jump, that's a trigger," he said.
OL,8,F"Cold is a big thing, so winter time
OL,9,Fis a terrible time for me.
OL,11,F"It's difficult because you never know
OL,12,Fwhen it's going to happen. It's also
OL,13,Ffrustrating because there's not much
OL,14,Fawareness, even with medical
OL,15,Fprofessionals.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,335,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F334A1783703991
OL,3,CThe 'excruciating' reality of Stiff
OL,4,CPerson Syndrome
OL,6,F"They've never heard of the condition,
OL,7,Fso they don't know how to treat me.
OL,8,FI've been into A&E twice and it's the
OL,9,Fworst place possible because of all
OL,10,Fthe noise and they're so busy. I've
OL,11,Fjust got to accept this is my life
OL,12,Ffrom now on.
OL,14,F"And I try not to dwell on it too much
OL,15,Fbecause I think it would put me in a
OL,16,Fdark place."
OL,18,FSPS is incurable, but medication and
OL,19,Ftreatment can help manage symptoms.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,335,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F334A1783703991
OL,3,CThe 'excruciating' reality of Stiff
OL,4,CPerson Syndrome
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the Department of
OL,7,FHealth and Social Care said: "Stiff
OL,8,FPerson Syndrome is a devastating,
OL,9,Fcondition and our thoughts are with
OL,10,FIan and his family.
OL,12,F"We know people living with rare
OL,13,Fdiseases often endure long and
OL,14,Fdifficult journeys to diagnosis and
OL,15,Fhave very limited treatment options
OL,16,Favailable.
OL,26,@oD@^OUtD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,335,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F334A1783703991
OL,3,CThe 'excruciating' reality of Stiff
OL,4,CPerson Syndrome
OL,6,F"We are working with the NHS,
OL,7,Fclinicians, researchers and patient
OL,8,Fgroups to improve care and we will
OL,9,Fensure the voices and experiences of
OL,10,Fpatients help shape future progress."
OL,26,@nD@AOU
